From: 
To: 
Subject: RE: call from Maxwell attorneys 
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 2020 19:53:36 +0000 
Chris and Mark just called me a few minutes ago, wanting to generally check in and see if we wanted or needed anything 
from them. I said that as a general matter, in terms of status, the investigation is ongoing, and that I didn't have any 
additional information beyond that. On whether we needed anything, I said I would circle up with the team and get them 
an answer on that. Initially my thought was to say no, nothing needed from them right now, but now I wonder, do we 
want to issue any document subpoenas to GM? Photos, communications, journals, memo pads, financial records 
associated with Epstein, or anything else ... thoughts?? 
Assistant U.S. Attorney
